<createdBy>lindomi</createdBy>
<createdTime>2021-10-27 07:49:02 UTC</createdTime>
<commentInRDBMS><![CDATA[A Security position hedged by Over the counter (OTC) derivative is the combination of a Long/Short balance sheet recognised security position and an Over the counter (OTC) derivative as a hedge that indicates which (portion of a Long/short balance sheet recognised security position is hedged by which Over the counter (OTC) derivative (acting in the role of an Over the counter (OTC) derivative as a hedge).]]></commentInRDBMS>
